Money Stuff =0A Here=E2=80=99s a thing you can do: Research a company and d=
ecide that its stock looks =0Agood. Buy some stock. Go on social media, or =
television if you =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=
=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12468728&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525=
&p=3D01302025>=0A=0A=0A=0AShort rules=0A=0AHere=E2=80=99s a thing you can d=
o:=0A=0A * Research a company and decide that its stock looks good. =0A * B=
uy some stock. =0A * Go on social media, or television if you are famous en=
ough, and say =E2=80=9Cthis =0Astock looks good, and I have bought some.=E2=
=80=9D =0A * The stock will go up, as people see you on social media or tel=
evision and =0Asay =E2=80=9Coh that person knows about stocks, I should buy=
 some of that stock.=E2=80=9D =0A * You sell the stock and make a profit. =
=0AI mean, maybe you can=E2=80=99t do that. You need a reputation, and some=
 social media =0Afollowing and/or the ability to get on television, to pull=
