 margin: 16px 0;"> <li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Research a company and=
 decide that its stock looks good.</li> <li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">B=
uy some stock.</li> <li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Go on social media, o=
r television if you are famous enough, and say =E2=80=9Cthis stock looks go=
