tock.=E2=80=9D</li> <li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You sell the stock an=
d make a profit.</li> </ol> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I mean, maybe <em>=
you </em>can=E2=80=99t do that. You need a reputation, and some social medi=
a following and/or the ability to get on television, to pull this off. If y=
ou don=E2=80=99t have that, maybe you can bootstrap it. Go on X, tweet =E2=
=80=9Cthis stock looks good and here=E2=80=99s why,=E2=80=9D back it up wit=
h some good analysis and compelling detail, and maybe the stock goes up. (N=
ot because people read your posts, but because you=E2=80=99re right.) Do it=
 again next week. Keep doing it. Maybe someone will discover your X account=
 and say =E2=80=9Chey this person is good at picking stocks,=E2=80=9D and i=
